      1          /**
      2           *  @file       
      3           *
      4           *  @brief      Standard API for additional OS services - embOS implementation
      5           *
      6           *  @details    This module provides a standard interface for some additional OS services without a direct
      7           *              dependency to a specific OS (like embOS)
      8           *              Current services provided:
      9           *              - Thread switch suspend/resume to temporary protect a specific execution
     10           *                      from preemption by high priority threads - interrupts would not be suspended by this feature
     11           *              - Mutex (or Resource semaphores) that can be used by defining and using a mutex variable in the module
     12           *                NOTE:
     13           *                - Mutex variables have to be initialized at every reset and shall not be saved on NVData sections
     14           *                - Mutexes cannot be used on any interrupt handler, including 1ms execution
     15           *
     16           *                Example:
     17           *                      OSSERVICE_MUTEX_TYPE Module_Data_Mutex;
     18           *                      ... <in an Initialize function> ...
     19           *                      OsServices__MutexInitialize(&Module_Data_Mutex);
     20           *                      ... <in one of the handlers, to protect execution through mutex>
     21           *                      OsServices__MutexLock(&Module_Data_Mutex);
     22           *                          ... do something...
     23           *                      OsServices__MutexRelease(&Module_Data_Mutex);
     24           *
     25           *                      OsServices__MutexTryLock() can be used instead of OsServices__MutexLock() to avoid waiting
     26           *                      before mutex is released; in this case the function returns FAIL.
     27           *
     28           *  @section    Applicable_Documents
     29           *					List here all the applicable documents if needed. <tr>	
     30           *
     31           *  @copyright  Copyright 2021. Whirlpool Corporation. All rights reserved - CONFIDENTIAL
     32           */
